{
  "stem": "18670.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I wasn't used to have to get tickets.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I found out different.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In America, you got those tickets.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I guess in Belgium you had to have a ticket too.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I walked out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I did fast.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I didn't get into any temple on Yom Kippur.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I met Jewish people later on, became friendly with.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we used to-- when they started rounding up refugees, we used to get up early in the morning, go to the forest if the weather was nice, and I spent the day in the forest.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I come back at night.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I always told my brother, if we go to sleep, never leave the key when you lock the door on the inside, because if somebody looks through the keyhole, you see a key, they know you have to be inside.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You have to be.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If they knock on the door at any time, we just don't answer.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And if it wasn't-- if it was raining, we would go to a movie.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In those days, they had movies that's played continuously.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I think had in the United States too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You could go from one, you could sit there for four hours to watch movies.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Or we would hide in the bakery.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He used to keep his bags of flours on top of his ovens.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We would hide behind the flour bags.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Actually, it was more convenient to go to the movies.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was cheap too.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was only a couple of francs.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Jewish committee gave us 42 francs a week, which was very little, if you realized that $1 was worth 50 francs.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we got one meal.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Half of it went for rent.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We-- we got a room in that same house.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
